## 🤖 Agent Reference Table

| Agent | Layer | Primary Output | Cursor Prompt Prefix |
|---|---|---|---|
| Orchestrator | Planning | Task breakdown, delegation | `@orchestrator` |
| Design | Design & Structure | Styled JSX, token mapping | `@design` |
| Architecture | Design & Structure | Folder scaffold, routes | `@arch` |
| Component | Implementation | Typed React components | `@components` |
| State | Implementation | Zustand stores, hooks | `@state` |
| API | Implementation | TanStack Query hooks | `@api` |
| Test | Quality | Vitest/RTL/Playwright tests | `@tests` |
| A11y | Quality | WCAG 2.1 AA audit + fixes | `@a11y` |
| Performance | Quality | Bundle analysis, vitals | `@perf` |
| Review | Quality | PR description, gate pass | `@review` |

